WEBVTT

00:04:59.842 --> 00:05:02.652
so there are infections
moving across the world

00:05:02.652 --> 00:05:06.111
for which, out of the more
than 100 antibiotics

00:05:06.111 --> 00:05:08.340
available on the market,

00:05:08.340 --> 00:05:11.754
two drugs might work with side effects,

00:05:11.754 --> 00:05:14.238
or one drug,

00:05:14.238 --> 00:05:15.646
or none.

00:05:16.096 --> 00:05:17.668
This is what that looks like.

00:05:18.278 --> 00:05:22.458
In 2000, the Centers for Disease
Control and Prevention, the CDC,

00:05:22.458 --> 00:05:24.501
identified a single case

00:05:24.501 --> 00:05:26.753
in a hospital in North Carolina

00:05:26.753 --> 00:05:30.486
of an infection resistant
to all but two drugs.